---
title : "Search"
permalink : "/docs/search/"
---

Jiraline gives issues search ability. You can search via certain fields or use JQL. The schema is presented below:

```bash
jiraline search <options>
```

Availible options are:

* -a (--assignee)
* -p (--project)
* -s (--status)
* -j (--jql)
* -n (--number) number of results